The paper discusses the energy efficiency and sustainable development of wireless communications, which falls under the category of network and information theory (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the tradeoffs between different parameters such as delay, power, bandwidth, and spectrum efficiency, which could be categorized under information theory (cs.IT) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the progress and challenges of 4G and 5G communications, which could be categorized under computer architecture and embedded systems (cs.AR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
